11 Marktgasse, 3800 Interlaken, Switzerland

Book a room

Right in the heart of Interlaken, STUDIO JOHN Interlaken has city views from the patio. This property offers access to a balcony, free private parking and free WiFi. The apartment features 1 bedroom, 1 bathroom, bed linen, towels, a flat-screen TV, a fully equipped kitchen, and a terrace with garden views. Hiking can be enjoyed nearby. Grindelwald Terminal is 19 km from the apartment, while Giessbachf√§lle is 22 km from the property. The nearest airport is Zurich Airport, 132 km from STUDIO JOHN Interlaken.
